{"doc":{"body":"<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content\" typography=\"classic\"><p id=\"u70d1aa81\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">幽灵依赖（Phantom Dependency）是指项目中</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">直接使用</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">了某个 npm 包，但这个包并未在 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">package.json</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 中显式声明为依赖。由于该包被其他已声明的依赖所依赖（即作为间接依赖），因此当前项目的 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">node_modules</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 中确实存在它，代码可以正常运行。然而一旦间接依赖升级或删除该包，项目就会因为找不到模块而崩溃。</span></p><h2 id=\"L0kdb\"><span class=\"ne-text\">幽灵依赖的危害</span></h2><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u6f3c47b4\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">项目脆弱性</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：构建或运行随时可能因依赖树变化而失败。</span></li><li id=\"u16c64fff\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">可维护性差</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：新加入的开发者无法从 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">package.json</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 获知项目的真实依赖。</span></li><li id=\"u5d74417c\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">版本不确定性</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：幽灵依赖的版本由间接依赖锁定，不受项目直接控制，可能导致难以追踪的 bug。</span></li></ul><h2 id=\"tO54l\"><span class=\"ne-text\">避免幽灵依赖的实践</span></h2><h3 id=\"w40HD\"><span class=\"ne-text\">1. 使用严格的包管理工具（如 pnpm）</span></h3><p id=\"u04dd4173\" class=\"ne-p\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">pnpm</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\"> 通过符号链接和严格的 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">node_modules</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 结构，</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">默认禁止访问未声明的依赖</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">。在 pnpm 的 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">node_modules</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 中，项目只能直接引用 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">package.json</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 中声明的依赖，而无法访问间接依赖，从而从根源上杜绝幽灵依赖。</span></p><pre data-language=\"bash\" id=\"fTEi7\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-bash\"><code># 安装 pnpm\nnpm install -g pnpm\n# 使用 pnpm 安装依赖\npnpm install</code></pre><p id=\"u96a1323e\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">如果代码中引入了未声明的包，运行时就会报错 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Error: Cannot find module 'xxx'</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，迫使开发者显式添加依赖。</span></p><h3 id=\"Q9BqO\"><span class=\"ne-text\">2. 借助工具进行静态检测</span></h3><h4 id=\"vcREt\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">eslint-plugin-import</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 的 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">import/no-extraneous-dependencies</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 规则</span></h4><p id=\"u8d7d6d7d\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">该规则会检查所有 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">import</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 语句，确保导入的模块在 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">package.json</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 的 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">dependencies</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">、</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">devDependencies</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 或 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">peerDependencies</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 中声明。</span></p><pre data-language=\"json\" id=\"CWxA9\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-json\"><code>// .eslintrc.js\nmodule.exports = {\n  plugins: ['import'],\n  rules: {\n    'import/no-extraneous-dependencies': [\n      'error',\n      {\n        devDependencies: ['**/*.test.js', '**/*.spec.js'], // 允许测试文件使用 devDependencies\n        peerDependencies: true, // 允许使用 peerDependencies\n      },\n    ],\n  },\n};</code></pre><h4 id=\"hM8NF\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">depcheck</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 工具</span></h4><p id=\"u9ae0e28a\" class=\"ne-p\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">depcheck</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 可以扫描项目，找出 </span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">未使用的依赖</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\"> 和 </span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">未声明的依赖</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">。</span></p><pre data-language=\"bash\" id=\"SMTsm\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-bash\"><code>npx depcheck</code></pre><p id=\"u2459cdc0\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">它会列出：</span></p><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"uc3fca1dc\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Unused dependencies</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">：在 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">package.json</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 中声明但代码中没有用到的包。</span></li><li id=\"ub92fce23\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Missing dependencies</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">：代码中使用但未在 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">package.json</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 中声明的包（即幽灵依赖）。</span></li></ul><p id=\"ua84196c4\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">建议将 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">depcheck</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 集成到 CI 流程中，防止幽灵依赖混入代码库。</span></p><h3 id=\"wAXCb\"><span class=\"ne-text\">3. 代码审查与规范</span></h3><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u17541ba5\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">在 Code Review 中强制要求</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：每当引入一个新的 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">import</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，必须确保对应的包已在 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">package.json</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 中。</span></li><li id=\"u262e1c72\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">使用依赖检测机器人</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：例如 Dependabot 或 Renovate，它们不仅能更新依赖，有时也能标记可疑的依赖使用。</span></li><li id=\"ua8e79556\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">制定团队规范</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：明确所有直接依赖必须显式声明，禁止利用间接依赖。</span></li></ul><h3 id=\"v6WaP\"><span class=\"ne-text\">4. 构建工具配置辅助</span></h3><p id=\"u81d447b7\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">虽然构建工具（Webpack、Vite）本身不直接阻止幽灵依赖，但可以通过一些配置辅助发现问题：</span></p><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"ub8547880\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">在 Webpack 中开启 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">resolve.fallback</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 时，如果使用了未声明的 Node.js 核心模块，可能会暴露幽灵依赖，但这不是主要手段。</span></li><li id=\"uec8661af\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">更推荐在 </span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">打包前</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\"> 通过 ESLint 或 depcheck 拦截问题。</span></li></ul><h3 id=\"A7uW6\"><span class=\"ne-text\">5. 依赖锁文件与定期清理</span></h3><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u8db89784\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">提交锁文件</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">（</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">package-lock.json</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> / </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">yarn.lock</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> / </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">pnpm-lock.yaml</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">）确保可重现的安装。</span></li><li id=\"u57e817aa\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">定期运行 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">npm prune</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 或 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">yarn dedupe</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 清理冗余依赖，但注意这并不能检测幽灵依赖，需要配合工具。</span></li></ul><h3 id=\"qDOR8\"><span class=\"ne-text\">6. 使用 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">exports</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 限制导入路径</span></h3><p id=\"ud402d70c\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">在库项目中，通过 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">package.json</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 的 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">exports</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 字段限制外部只能访问特定的入口文件，可以间接避免使用者通过幽灵依赖访问内部模块。但这主要是控制 API 边界，并非直接解决幽灵依赖问题。</span></p><h2 id=\"uktEd\"><span class=\"ne-text\">推荐组合实践</span></h2><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u384fe1cb\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">开发环境</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：使用 pnpm 作为包管理器 + ESLint </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">import/no-extraneous-dependencies</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 规则实时提示。</span></li><li id=\"u733dd538\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">CI 环境</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：运行 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">depcheck</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 或 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">eslint</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 检查，确保没有幽灵依赖。</span></li><li id=\"uf1a88790\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">定期维护</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：每月执行一次 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">depcheck</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 并清理未使用的依赖。</span></li></ul><p id=\"u77f3cbc5\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">通过这些实践，可以大大降低项目对幽灵依赖的隐性依赖，使依赖关系清晰、构建稳定，提高代码的可维护性和可移植性。</span></p></div>","body_asl":"<!doctype lake><meta name=\"doc-version\" content=\"1\" /><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"fixed\" /><meta name=\"typography\" content=\"classic\" /><meta name=\"paragraphSpacing\" content=\"relax\" /><p data-lake-id=\"u70d1aa81\" id=\"u70d1aa81\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3184c482\" id=\"u3184c482\">幽灵依赖（Phantom Dependency）是指项目中</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uc11c398d\" id=\"uc11c398d\">直接使用</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ufecabacb\" id=\"ufecabacb\">了某个 npm 包，但这个包并未在 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u92a1ae75\" id=\"u92a1ae75\"><span data-lake-id=\"u8b8532ca\" id=\"u8b8532ca\">package.json</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u8c36c54f\" id=\"u8c36c54f\"> 中显式声明为依赖。由于该包被其他已声明的依赖所依赖（即作为间接依赖），因此当前项目的 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ue9ff324f\" id=\"ue9ff324f\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6d52dea3\" id=\"u6d52dea3\">node_modules</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ua21cfdc4\" id=\"ua21cfdc4\"> 中确实存在它，代码可以正常运行。然而一旦间接依赖升级或删除该包，项目就会因为找不到模块而崩溃。</span></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"L0kdb\" id=\"L0kdb\"><span data-lake-id=\"uff1713a0\" id=\"uff1713a0\">幽灵依赖的危害</span></h2><ul list=\"u50805e13\"><li fid=\"udd324b1a\" data-lake-id=\"u6f3c47b4\" id=\"u6f3c47b4\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u1f11f563\" id=\"u1f11f563\">项目脆弱性</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"uf3336a2e\" id=\"uf3336a2e\">：构建或运行随时可能因依赖树变化而失败。</span></li><li fid=\"udd324b1a\" data-lake-id=\"u16c64fff\" id=\"u16c64fff\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u799ccd9e\" id=\"u799ccd9e\">可维护性差</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u221501d0\" id=\"u221501d0\">：新加入的开发者无法从 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u2f346349\" id=\"u2f346349\"><span data-lake-id=\"u63cb2e18\" id=\"u63cb2e18\">package.json</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u6b7eb869\" id=\"u6b7eb869\"> 获知项目的真实依赖。</span></li><li fid=\"udd324b1a\" data-lake-id=\"u5d74417c\" id=\"u5d74417c\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u88b4fd8e\" id=\"u88b4fd8e\">版本不确定性</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u8aa4b97b\" id=\"u8aa4b97b\">：幽灵依赖的版本由间接依赖锁定，不受项目直接控制，可能导致难以追踪的 bug。</span></li></ul><h2 data-lake-id=\"tO54l\" id=\"tO54l\"><span data-lake-id=\"u8a0e049f\" id=\"u8a0e049f\">避免幽灵依赖的实践</span></h2><h3 data-lake-id=\"w40HD\" id=\"w40HD\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6da16610\" id=\"u6da16610\">1. 使用严格的包管理工具（如 pnpm）</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u04dd4173\" id=\"u04dd4173\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u31808e5a\" id=\"u31808e5a\">pnpm</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u04878f97\" id=\"u04878f97\"> 通过符号链接和严格的 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ud1fdbac1\" id=\"ud1fdbac1\"><span data-lake-id=\"u33be59b2\" id=\"u33be59b2\">node_modules</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u1533c4c4\" id=\"u1533c4c4\"> 结构，</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ub811551e\" id=\"ub811551e\">默认禁止访问未声明的依赖</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u2b8f529b\" id=\"u2b8f529b\">。在 pnpm 的 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u834f164a\" id=\"u834f164a\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub461dcbe\" id=\"ub461dcbe\">node_modules</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u970d1b49\" id=\"u970d1b49\"> 中，项目只能直接引用 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u484d34ee\" id=\"u484d34ee\"><span data-lake-id=\"u957d6fa0\" id=\"u957d6fa0\">package.json</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ub5f70d3e\" id=\"ub5f70d3e\"> 中声明的依赖，而无法访问间接依赖，从而从根源上杜绝幽灵依赖。</span></p><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22bash%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%20pnpm%5Cnnpm%20install%20-g%20pnpm%5Cn%23%20%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%20pnpm%20%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E4%BE%9D%E8%B5%96%5Cnpnpm%20install%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22fTEi7%22%7D\"></card><p data-lake-id=\"u96a1323e\" id=\"u96a1323e\"><span data-lake-id=\"uaa8ddcb1\" id=\"uaa8ddcb1\">如果代码中引入了未声明的包，运行时就会报错 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u61a273c6\" id=\"u61a273c6\"><span data-lake-id=\"u9e07985e\" id=\"u9e07985e\">Error: Cannot find module 'xxx'</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ucf4859b1\" id=\"ucf4859b1\">，迫使开发者显式添加依赖。</span></p><h3 data-lake-id=\"Q9BqO\" id=\"Q9BqO\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6a8f0190\" id=\"u6a8f0190\">2. 借助工具进行静态检测</span></h3><h4 data-lake-id=\"vcREt\" id=\"vcREt\"><code data-lake-id=\"u0b8348a9\" id=\"u0b8348a9\"><span data-lake-id=\"u1c6d846a\" id=\"u1c6d846a\">eslint-plugin-import</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u193d6126\" id=\"u193d6126\"> 的 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u11e31b14\" id=\"u11e31b14\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf02823e1\" id=\"uf02823e1\">import/no-extraneous-dependencies</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u19d91b1f\" id=\"u19d91b1f\"> 规则</span></h4><p data-lake-id=\"u8d7d6d7d\" id=\"u8d7d6d7d\"><span data-lake-id=\"u0a5d1da6\" id=\"u0a5d1da6\">该规则会检查所有 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ua1d8e479\" id=\"ua1d8e479\"><span data-lake-id=\"u9e69c9a1\" id=\"u9e69c9a1\">import</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u3ff0c774\" id=\"u3ff0c774\"> 语句，确保导入的模块在 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u9df74133\" id=\"u9df74133\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3a1b6608\" id=\"u3a1b6608\">package.json</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u8d48da7e\" id=\"u8d48da7e\"> 的 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ufccae11d\" id=\"ufccae11d\"><span data-lake-id=\"ucd515691\" id=\"ucd515691\">dependencies</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u916657df\" id=\"u916657df\">、</span><code data-lake-id=\"ueda2d7df\" id=\"ueda2d7df\"><span data-lake-id=\"u8cb6936c\" id=\"u8cb6936c\">devDependencies</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"udcbe9542\" id=\"udcbe9542\"> 或 </span><code data-lake-id=\"uf45636c7\" id=\"uf45636c7\"><span data-lake-id=\"u53a37c01\" id=\"u53a37c01\">peerDependencies</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uc38d276a\" id=\"uc38d276a\"> 中声明。</span></p><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22json%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%2F%2F%20.eslintrc.js%5Cnmodule.exports%20%3D%20%7B%5Cn%20%20plugins%3A%20%5B'import'%5D%2C%5Cn%20%20rules%3A%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20'import%2Fno-extraneous-dependencies'%3A%20%5B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20'error'%2C%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20devDependencies%3A%20%5B'**%2F*.test.js'%2C%20'**%2F*.spec.js'%5D%2C%20%2F%2F%20%E5%85%81%E8%AE%B8%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%20devDependencies%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20peerDependencies%3A%20true%2C%20%2F%2F%20%E5%85%81%E8%AE%B8%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%20peerDependencies%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%7D%2C%5Cn%20%20%20%20%5D%2C%5Cn%20%20%7D%2C%5Cn%7D%3B%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22CWxA9%22%7D\"></card><h4 data-lake-id=\"hM8NF\" id=\"hM8NF\"><code data-lake-id=\"u0cff2b43\" id=\"u0cff2b43\"><span data-lake-id=\"u195a3878\" id=\"u195a3878\">depcheck</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u0f44923c\" id=\"u0f44923c\"> 工具</span></h4><p data-lake-id=\"u9ae0e28a\" id=\"u9ae0e28a\"><code data-lake-id=\"uf5494104\" id=\"uf5494104\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf5181803\" id=\"uf5181803\">depcheck</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"udbb56eeb\" id=\"udbb56eeb\"> 可以扫描项目，找出 </span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u62e6388d\" id=\"u62e6388d\">未使用的依赖</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u398813d4\" id=\"u398813d4\"> 和 </span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ue488ae85\" id=\"ue488ae85\">未声明的依赖</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"uc0a3aee2\" id=\"uc0a3aee2\">。</span></p><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22bash%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22npx%20depcheck%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22SMTsm%22%7D\"></card><p data-lake-id=\"u2459cdc0\" id=\"u2459cdc0\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf26fb7a9\" id=\"uf26fb7a9\">它会列出：</span></p><ul list=\"u94b47b84\"><li fid=\"u04866b68\" data-lake-id=\"uc3fca1dc\" id=\"uc3fca1dc\"><code data-lake-id=\"u96bb2458\" id=\"u96bb2458\"><span data-lake-id=\"ud3282102\" id=\"ud3282102\">Unused dependencies</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u909df66e\" id=\"u909df66e\">：在 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u690ea683\" id=\"u690ea683\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3f88864c\" id=\"u3f88864c\">package.json</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u4a42cae3\" id=\"u4a42cae3\"> 中声明但代码中没有用到的包。</span></li><li fid=\"u04866b68\" data-lake-id=\"ub92fce23\" id=\"ub92fce23\"><code data-lake-id=\"ude3f8626\" id=\"ude3f8626\"><span data-lake-id=\"uda7a8b9c\" id=\"uda7a8b9c\">Missing dependencies</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u100bb3d4\" id=\"u100bb3d4\">：代码中使用但未在 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u079aa073\" id=\"u079aa073\"><span data-lake-id=\"u223e99b8\" id=\"u223e99b8\">package.json</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ucf3c8755\" id=\"ucf3c8755\"> 中声明的包（即幽灵依赖）。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"ua84196c4\" id=\"ua84196c4\"><span data-lake-id=\"u341979c3\" id=\"u341979c3\">建议将 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u2684919c\" id=\"u2684919c\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5cf6bd77\" id=\"u5cf6bd77\">depcheck</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u4f154de6\" id=\"u4f154de6\"> 集成到 CI 流程中，防止幽灵依赖混入代码库。</span></p><h3 data-lake-id=\"wAXCb\" id=\"wAXCb\"><span data-lake-id=\"uc2fad333\" id=\"uc2fad333\">3. 代码审查与规范</span></h3><ul list=\"u09ed0124\"><li fid=\"u85c485be\" data-lake-id=\"u17541ba5\" id=\"u17541ba5\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u47548657\" id=\"u47548657\">在 Code Review 中强制要求</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u62f38c45\" id=\"u62f38c45\">：每当引入一个新的 </span><code data-lake-id=\"udacf0801\" id=\"udacf0801\"><span data-lake-id=\"u67c1d02e\" id=\"u67c1d02e\">import</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u8c95a5e2\" id=\"u8c95a5e2\">，必须确保对应的包已在 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u9f8fd27f\" id=\"u9f8fd27f\"><span data-lake-id=\"u8439db94\" id=\"u8439db94\">package.json</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ub22d1928\" id=\"ub22d1928\"> 中。</span></li><li fid=\"u85c485be\" data-lake-id=\"u262e1c72\" id=\"u262e1c72\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uee0aea94\" id=\"uee0aea94\">使用依赖检测机器人</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u39c429fc\" id=\"u39c429fc\">：例如 Dependabot 或 Renovate，它们不仅能更新依赖，有时也能标记可疑的依赖使用。</span></li><li fid=\"u85c485be\" data-lake-id=\"ua8e79556\" id=\"ua8e79556\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u04562a15\" id=\"u04562a15\">制定团队规范</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u736c160f\" id=\"u736c160f\">：明确所有直接依赖必须显式声明，禁止利用间接依赖。</span></li></ul><h3 data-lake-id=\"v6WaP\" id=\"v6WaP\"><span data-lake-id=\"u740a9ef2\" id=\"u740a9ef2\">4. 构建工具配置辅助</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u81d447b7\" id=\"u81d447b7\"><span data-lake-id=\"u48f385fe\" id=\"u48f385fe\">虽然构建工具（Webpack、Vite）本身不直接阻止幽灵依赖，但可以通过一些配置辅助发现问题：</span></p><ul list=\"uf877d7cc\"><li fid=\"ud8d9513f\" data-lake-id=\"ub8547880\" id=\"ub8547880\"><span data-lake-id=\"u034f0ebc\" id=\"u034f0ebc\">在 Webpack 中开启 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u6b3ae48c\" id=\"u6b3ae48c\"><span data-lake-id=\"u7a2d20d4\" id=\"u7a2d20d4\">resolve.fallback</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u40b07539\" id=\"u40b07539\"> 时，如果使用了未声明的 Node.js 核心模块，可能会暴露幽灵依赖，但这不是主要手段。</span></li><li fid=\"ud8d9513f\" data-lake-id=\"uec8661af\" id=\"uec8661af\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue342eb93\" id=\"ue342eb93\">更推荐在 </span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ue2d1928c\" id=\"ue2d1928c\">打包前</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u38ce3793\" id=\"u38ce3793\"> 通过 ESLint 或 depcheck 拦截问题。</span></li></ul><h3 data-lake-id=\"A7uW6\" id=\"A7uW6\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3db4b4dd\" id=\"u3db4b4dd\">5. 依赖锁文件与定期清理</span></h3><ul list=\"u51d0ed26\"><li fid=\"u35096e3e\" data-lake-id=\"u8db89784\" id=\"u8db89784\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ued79f3e9\" id=\"ued79f3e9\">提交锁文件</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ue58f4c7b\" id=\"ue58f4c7b\">（</span><code data-lake-id=\"u2ad6e61e\" id=\"u2ad6e61e\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue742c179\" id=\"ue742c179\">package-lock.json</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ue1a17a66\" id=\"ue1a17a66\"> / </span><code data-lake-id=\"ue68704ee\" id=\"ue68704ee\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub13db963\" id=\"ub13db963\">yarn.lock</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u6c5a2009\" id=\"u6c5a2009\"> / </span><code data-lake-id=\"u32172217\" id=\"u32172217\"><span data-lake-id=\"ua1fd3195\" id=\"ua1fd3195\">pnpm-lock.yaml</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u4dc619de\" id=\"u4dc619de\">）确保可重现的安装。</span></li><li fid=\"u35096e3e\" data-lake-id=\"u57e817aa\" id=\"u57e817aa\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3bd9e726\" id=\"u3bd9e726\">定期运行 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u831e5f7d\" id=\"u831e5f7d\"><span data-lake-id=\"u97c13af1\" id=\"u97c13af1\">npm prune</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u5ba9c320\" id=\"u5ba9c320\"> 或 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u85464fe3\" id=\"u85464fe3\"><span data-lake-id=\"u41288d1f\" id=\"u41288d1f\">yarn dedupe</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ufb1b87db\" id=\"ufb1b87db\"> 清理冗余依赖，但注意这并不能检测幽灵依赖，需要配合工具。</span></li></ul><h3 data-lake-id=\"qDOR8\" id=\"qDOR8\"><span data-lake-id=\"u95812139\" id=\"u95812139\">6. 使用 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u868e8fe8\" id=\"u868e8fe8\"><span data-lake-id=\"u16a5ffc2\" id=\"u16a5ffc2\">exports</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u273c1258\" id=\"u273c1258\"> 限制导入路径</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"ud402d70c\" id=\"ud402d70c\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4462d11f\" id=\"u4462d11f\">在库项目中，通过 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u6fa439f7\" id=\"u6fa439f7\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5a1a9e9a\" id=\"u5a1a9e9a\">package.json</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u3f140646\" id=\"u3f140646\"> 的 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u3dd5d368\" id=\"u3dd5d368\"><span data-lake-id=\"u72ccf01a\" id=\"u72ccf01a\">exports</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uf7472868\" id=\"uf7472868\"> 字段限制外部只能访问特定的入口文件，可以间接避免使用者通过幽灵依赖访问内部模块。但这主要是控制 API 边界，并非直接解决幽灵依赖问题。</span></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"uktEd\" id=\"uktEd\"><span data-lake-id=\"ud34407f6\" id=\"ud34407f6\">推荐组合实践</span></h2><ul list=\"u3bba896a\"><li fid=\"u00fc4f71\" data-lake-id=\"u384fe1cb\" id=\"u384fe1cb\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u3e941e36\" id=\"u3e941e36\">开发环境</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u13771dd6\" id=\"u13771dd6\">：使用 pnpm 作为包管理器 + ESLint </span><code data-lake-id=\"uebf1c54d\" id=\"uebf1c54d\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4b59f92b\" id=\"u4b59f92b\">import/no-extraneous-dependencies</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ud174a0b2\" id=\"ud174a0b2\"> 规则实时提示。</span></li><li fid=\"u00fc4f71\" data-lake-id=\"u733dd538\" id=\"u733dd538\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ue380c957\" id=\"ue380c957\">CI 环境</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u455f3d8b\" id=\"u455f3d8b\">：运行 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u467e2158\" id=\"u467e2158\"><span data-lake-id=\"uee44f745\" id=\"uee44f745\">depcheck</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u695a74f4\" id=\"u695a74f4\"> 或 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u97c93672\" id=\"u97c93672\"><span data-lake-id=\"ubb71c6a4\" id=\"ubb71c6a4\">eslint</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u854eb50b\" id=\"u854eb50b\"> 检查，确保没有幽灵依赖。</span></li><li fid=\"u00fc4f71\" data-lake-id=\"uf1a88790\" id=\"uf1a88790\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u6959aa79\" id=\"u6959aa79\">定期维护</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u244e2094\" id=\"u244e2094\">：每月执行一次 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u037e73a4\" id=\"u037e73a4\"><span data-lake-id=\"u180679e4\" id=\"u180679e4\">depcheck</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u57938ce1\" id=\"u57938ce1\"> 并清理未使用的依赖。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"u77f3cbc5\" id=\"u77f3cbc5\"><span data-lake-id=\"u91af23ef\" id=\"u91af23ef\">通过这些实践，可以大大降低项目对幽灵依赖的隐性依赖，使依赖关系清晰、构建稳定，提高代码的可维护性和可移植性。</span></p>","body_draft":"<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content\" typography=\"classic\"><p id=\"u70d1aa81\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">幽灵依赖（Phantom Dependency）是指项目中</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">直接使用</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">了某个 npm 包，但这个包并未在 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">package.json</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 中显式声明为依赖。由于该包被其他已声明的依赖所依赖（即作为间接依赖），因此当前项目的 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">node_modules</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 中确实存在它，代码可以正常运行。然而一旦间接依赖升级或删除该包，项目就会因为找不到模块而崩溃。</span></p><h2 id=\"L0kdb\"><span class=\"ne-text\">幽灵依赖的危害</span></h2><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u6f3c47b4\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">项目脆弱性</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：构建或运行随时可能因依赖树变化而失败。</span></li><li id=\"u16c64fff\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">可维护性差</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：新加入的开发者无法从 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">package.json</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 获知项目的真实依赖。</span></li><li id=\"u5d74417c\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">版本不确定性</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：幽灵依赖的版本由间接依赖锁定，不受项目直接控制，可能导致难以追踪的 bug。</span></li></ul><h2 id=\"tO54l\"><span class=\"ne-text\">避免幽灵依赖的实践</span></h2><h3 id=\"w40HD\"><span class=\"ne-text\">1. 使用严格的包管理工具（如 pnpm）</span></h3><p id=\"u04dd4173\" class=\"ne-p\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">pnpm</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\"> 通过符号链接和严格的 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">node_modules</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 结构，</span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">默认禁止访问未声明的依赖</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">。在 pnpm 的 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">node_modules</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 中，项目只能直接引用 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">package.json</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 中声明的依赖，而无法访问间接依赖，从而从根源上杜绝幽灵依赖。</span></p><pre data-language=\"bash\" id=\"fTEi7\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-bash\"><code># 安装 pnpm\nnpm install -g pnpm\n# 使用 pnpm 安装依赖\npnpm install</code></pre><p id=\"u96a1323e\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">如果代码中引入了未声明的包，运行时就会报错 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Error: Cannot find module 'xxx'</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，迫使开发者显式添加依赖。</span></p><h3 id=\"Q9BqO\"><span class=\"ne-text\">2. 借助工具进行静态检测</span></h3><h4 id=\"vcREt\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">eslint-plugin-import</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 的 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">import/no-extraneous-dependencies</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 规则</span></h4><p id=\"u8d7d6d7d\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">该规则会检查所有 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">import</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 语句，确保导入的模块在 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">package.json</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 的 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">dependencies</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">、</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">devDependencies</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 或 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">peerDependencies</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 中声明。</span></p><pre data-language=\"json\" id=\"CWxA9\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-json\"><code>// .eslintrc.js\nmodule.exports = {\n  plugins: ['import'],\n  rules: {\n    'import/no-extraneous-dependencies': [\n      'error',\n      {\n        devDependencies: ['**/*.test.js', '**/*.spec.js'], // 允许测试文件使用 devDependencies\n        peerDependencies: true, // 允许使用 peerDependencies\n      },\n    ],\n  },\n};</code></pre><h4 id=\"hM8NF\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">depcheck</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 工具</span></h4><p id=\"u9ae0e28a\" class=\"ne-p\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">depcheck</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 可以扫描项目，找出 </span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">未使用的依赖</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\"> 和 </span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">未声明的依赖</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">。</span></p><pre data-language=\"bash\" id=\"SMTsm\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-bash\"><code>npx depcheck</code></pre><p id=\"u2459cdc0\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">它会列出：</span></p><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"uc3fca1dc\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Unused dependencies</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">：在 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">package.json</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 中声明但代码中没有用到的包。</span></li><li id=\"ub92fce23\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Missing dependencies</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">：代码中使用但未在 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">package.json</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 中声明的包（即幽灵依赖）。</span></li></ul><p id=\"ua84196c4\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">建议将 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">depcheck</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 集成到 CI 流程中，防止幽灵依赖混入代码库。</span></p><h3 id=\"wAXCb\"><span class=\"ne-text\">3. 代码审查与规范</span></h3><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u17541ba5\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">在 Code Review 中强制要求</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：每当引入一个新的 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">import</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">，必须确保对应的包已在 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">package.json</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 中。</span></li><li id=\"u262e1c72\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">使用依赖检测机器人</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：例如 Dependabot 或 Renovate，它们不仅能更新依赖，有时也能标记可疑的依赖使用。</span></li><li id=\"ua8e79556\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">制定团队规范</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：明确所有直接依赖必须显式声明，禁止利用间接依赖。</span></li></ul><h3 id=\"v6WaP\"><span class=\"ne-text\">4. 构建工具配置辅助</span></h3><p id=\"u81d447b7\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">虽然构建工具（Webpack、Vite）本身不直接阻止幽灵依赖，但可以通过一些配置辅助发现问题：</span></p><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"ub8547880\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">在 Webpack 中开启 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">resolve.fallback</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 时，如果使用了未声明的 Node.js 核心模块，可能会暴露幽灵依赖，但这不是主要手段。</span></li><li id=\"uec8661af\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">更推荐在 </span><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">打包前</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\"> 通过 ESLint 或 depcheck 拦截问题。</span></li></ul><h3 id=\"A7uW6\"><span class=\"ne-text\">5. 依赖锁文件与定期清理</span></h3><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u8db89784\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">提交锁文件</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">（</span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">package-lock.json</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> / </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">yarn.lock</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> / </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">pnpm-lock.yaml</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\">）确保可重现的安装。</span></li><li id=\"u57e817aa\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">定期运行 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">npm prune</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 或 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">yarn dedupe</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 清理冗余依赖，但注意这并不能检测幽灵依赖，需要配合工具。</span></li></ul><h3 id=\"qDOR8\"><span class=\"ne-text\">6. 使用 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">exports</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 限制导入路径</span></h3><p id=\"ud402d70c\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">在库项目中，通过 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">package.json</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 的 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">exports</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 字段限制外部只能访问特定的入口文件，可以间接避免使用者通过幽灵依赖访问内部模块。但这主要是控制 API 边界，并非直接解决幽灵依赖问题。</span></p><h2 id=\"uktEd\"><span class=\"ne-text\">推荐组合实践</span></h2><ul class=\"ne-ul\"><li id=\"u384fe1cb\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">开发环境</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：使用 pnpm 作为包管理器 + ESLint </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">import/no-extraneous-dependencies</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 规则实时提示。</span></li><li id=\"u733dd538\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">CI 环境</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：运行 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">depcheck</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 或 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">eslint</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 检查，确保没有幽灵依赖。</span></li><li id=\"uf1a88790\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><strong><span class=\"ne-text\">定期维护</span></strong><span class=\"ne-text\">：每月执行一次 </span><code class=\"ne-code\"><span class=\"ne-text\">depcheck</span></code><span class=\"ne-text\"> 并清理未使用的依赖。</span></li></ul><p id=\"u77f3cbc5\" class=\"ne-p\"><span class=\"ne-text\">通过这些实践，可以大大降低项目对幽灵依赖的隐性依赖，使依赖关系清晰、构建稳定，提高代码的可维护性和可移植性。</span></p></div>","body_draft_asl":"<!doctype lake><meta name=\"doc-version\" content=\"1\" /><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"fixed\" /><meta name=\"typography\" content=\"classic\" /><meta name=\"paragraphSpacing\" content=\"relax\" /><p data-lake-id=\"u70d1aa81\" id=\"u70d1aa81\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3184c482\" id=\"u3184c482\">幽灵依赖（Phantom Dependency）是指项目中</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uc11c398d\" id=\"uc11c398d\">直接使用</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ufecabacb\" id=\"ufecabacb\">了某个 npm 包，但这个包并未在 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u92a1ae75\" id=\"u92a1ae75\"><span data-lake-id=\"u8b8532ca\" id=\"u8b8532ca\">package.json</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u8c36c54f\" id=\"u8c36c54f\"> 中显式声明为依赖。由于该包被其他已声明的依赖所依赖（即作为间接依赖），因此当前项目的 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ue9ff324f\" id=\"ue9ff324f\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6d52dea3\" id=\"u6d52dea3\">node_modules</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ua21cfdc4\" id=\"ua21cfdc4\"> 中确实存在它，代码可以正常运行。然而一旦间接依赖升级或删除该包，项目就会因为找不到模块而崩溃。</span></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"L0kdb\" id=\"L0kdb\"><span data-lake-id=\"uff1713a0\" id=\"uff1713a0\">幽灵依赖的危害</span></h2><ul list=\"u50805e13\"><li fid=\"udd324b1a\" data-lake-id=\"u6f3c47b4\" id=\"u6f3c47b4\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u1f11f563\" id=\"u1f11f563\">项目脆弱性</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"uf3336a2e\" id=\"uf3336a2e\">：构建或运行随时可能因依赖树变化而失败。</span></li><li fid=\"udd324b1a\" data-lake-id=\"u16c64fff\" id=\"u16c64fff\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u799ccd9e\" id=\"u799ccd9e\">可维护性差</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u221501d0\" id=\"u221501d0\">：新加入的开发者无法从 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u2f346349\" id=\"u2f346349\"><span data-lake-id=\"u63cb2e18\" id=\"u63cb2e18\">package.json</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u6b7eb869\" id=\"u6b7eb869\"> 获知项目的真实依赖。</span></li><li fid=\"udd324b1a\" data-lake-id=\"u5d74417c\" id=\"u5d74417c\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u88b4fd8e\" id=\"u88b4fd8e\">版本不确定性</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u8aa4b97b\" id=\"u8aa4b97b\">：幽灵依赖的版本由间接依赖锁定，不受项目直接控制，可能导致难以追踪的 bug。</span></li></ul><h2 data-lake-id=\"tO54l\" id=\"tO54l\"><span data-lake-id=\"u8a0e049f\" id=\"u8a0e049f\">避免幽灵依赖的实践</span></h2><h3 data-lake-id=\"w40HD\" id=\"w40HD\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6da16610\" id=\"u6da16610\">1. 使用严格的包管理工具（如 pnpm）</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u04dd4173\" id=\"u04dd4173\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u31808e5a\" id=\"u31808e5a\">pnpm</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u04878f97\" id=\"u04878f97\"> 通过符号链接和严格的 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ud1fdbac1\" id=\"ud1fdbac1\"><span data-lake-id=\"u33be59b2\" id=\"u33be59b2\">node_modules</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u1533c4c4\" id=\"u1533c4c4\"> 结构，</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ub811551e\" id=\"ub811551e\">默认禁止访问未声明的依赖</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u2b8f529b\" id=\"u2b8f529b\">。在 pnpm 的 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u834f164a\" id=\"u834f164a\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub461dcbe\" id=\"ub461dcbe\">node_modules</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u970d1b49\" id=\"u970d1b49\"> 中，项目只能直接引用 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u484d34ee\" id=\"u484d34ee\"><span data-lake-id=\"u957d6fa0\" id=\"u957d6fa0\">package.json</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ub5f70d3e\" id=\"ub5f70d3e\"> 中声明的依赖，而无法访问间接依赖，从而从根源上杜绝幽灵依赖。</span></p><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22bash%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%20pnpm%5Cnnpm%20install%20-g%20pnpm%5Cn%23%20%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%20pnpm%20%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E4%BE%9D%E8%B5%96%5Cnpnpm%20install%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22fTEi7%22%7D\"></card><p data-lake-id=\"u96a1323e\" id=\"u96a1323e\"><span data-lake-id=\"uaa8ddcb1\" id=\"uaa8ddcb1\">如果代码中引入了未声明的包，运行时就会报错 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u61a273c6\" id=\"u61a273c6\"><span data-lake-id=\"u9e07985e\" id=\"u9e07985e\">Error: Cannot find module 'xxx'</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ucf4859b1\" id=\"ucf4859b1\">，迫使开发者显式添加依赖。</span></p><h3 data-lake-id=\"Q9BqO\" id=\"Q9BqO\"><span data-lake-id=\"u6a8f0190\" id=\"u6a8f0190\">2. 借助工具进行静态检测</span></h3><h4 data-lake-id=\"vcREt\" id=\"vcREt\"><code data-lake-id=\"u0b8348a9\" id=\"u0b8348a9\"><span data-lake-id=\"u1c6d846a\" id=\"u1c6d846a\">eslint-plugin-import</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u193d6126\" id=\"u193d6126\"> 的 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u11e31b14\" id=\"u11e31b14\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf02823e1\" id=\"uf02823e1\">import/no-extraneous-dependencies</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u19d91b1f\" id=\"u19d91b1f\"> 规则</span></h4><p data-lake-id=\"u8d7d6d7d\" id=\"u8d7d6d7d\"><span data-lake-id=\"u0a5d1da6\" id=\"u0a5d1da6\">该规则会检查所有 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ua1d8e479\" id=\"ua1d8e479\"><span data-lake-id=\"u9e69c9a1\" id=\"u9e69c9a1\">import</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u3ff0c774\" id=\"u3ff0c774\"> 语句，确保导入的模块在 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u9df74133\" id=\"u9df74133\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3a1b6608\" id=\"u3a1b6608\">package.json</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u8d48da7e\" id=\"u8d48da7e\"> 的 </span><code data-lake-id=\"ufccae11d\" id=\"ufccae11d\"><span data-lake-id=\"ucd515691\" id=\"ucd515691\">dependencies</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u916657df\" id=\"u916657df\">、</span><code data-lake-id=\"ueda2d7df\" id=\"ueda2d7df\"><span data-lake-id=\"u8cb6936c\" id=\"u8cb6936c\">devDependencies</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"udcbe9542\" id=\"udcbe9542\"> 或 </span><code data-lake-id=\"uf45636c7\" id=\"uf45636c7\"><span data-lake-id=\"u53a37c01\" id=\"u53a37c01\">peerDependencies</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uc38d276a\" id=\"uc38d276a\"> 中声明。</span></p><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22json%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%2F%2F%20.eslintrc.js%5Cnmodule.exports%20%3D%20%7B%5Cn%20%20plugins%3A%20%5B'import'%5D%2C%5Cn%20%20rules%3A%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20'import%2Fno-extraneous-dependencies'%3A%20%5B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20'error'%2C%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20devDependencies%3A%20%5B'**%2F*.test.js'%2C%20'**%2F*.spec.js'%5D%2C%20%2F%2F%20%E5%85%81%E8%AE%B8%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%20devDependencies%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20peerDependencies%3A%20true%2C%20%2F%2F%20%E5%85%81%E8%AE%B8%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%20peerDependencies%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%7D%2C%5Cn%20%20%20%20%5D%2C%5Cn%20%20%7D%2C%5Cn%7D%3B%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22CWxA9%22%7D\"></card><h4 data-lake-id=\"hM8NF\" id=\"hM8NF\"><code data-lake-id=\"u0cff2b43\" id=\"u0cff2b43\"><span data-lake-id=\"u195a3878\" id=\"u195a3878\">depcheck</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u0f44923c\" id=\"u0f44923c\"> 工具</span></h4><p data-lake-id=\"u9ae0e28a\" id=\"u9ae0e28a\"><code data-lake-id=\"uf5494104\" id=\"uf5494104\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf5181803\" id=\"uf5181803\">depcheck</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"udbb56eeb\" id=\"udbb56eeb\"> 可以扫描项目，找出 </span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u62e6388d\" id=\"u62e6388d\">未使用的依赖</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u398813d4\" id=\"u398813d4\"> 和 </span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ue488ae85\" id=\"ue488ae85\">未声明的依赖</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"uc0a3aee2\" id=\"uc0a3aee2\">。</span></p><card type=\"inline\" name=\"codeblock\" value=\"data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22mode%22%3A%22bash%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22npx%20depcheck%22%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22id%22%3A%22SMTsm%22%7D\"></card><p data-lake-id=\"u2459cdc0\" id=\"u2459cdc0\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf26fb7a9\" id=\"uf26fb7a9\">它会列出：</span></p><ul list=\"u94b47b84\"><li fid=\"u04866b68\" data-lake-id=\"uc3fca1dc\" id=\"uc3fca1dc\"><code data-lake-id=\"u96bb2458\" id=\"u96bb2458\"><span data-lake-id=\"ud3282102\" id=\"ud3282102\">Unused dependencies</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u909df66e\" id=\"u909df66e\">：在 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u690ea683\" id=\"u690ea683\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3f88864c\" id=\"u3f88864c\">package.json</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u4a42cae3\" id=\"u4a42cae3\"> 中声明但代码中没有用到的包。</span></li><li fid=\"u04866b68\" data-lake-id=\"ub92fce23\" id=\"ub92fce23\"><code data-lake-id=\"ude3f8626\" id=\"ude3f8626\"><span data-lake-id=\"uda7a8b9c\" id=\"uda7a8b9c\">Missing dependencies</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u100bb3d4\" id=\"u100bb3d4\">：代码中使用但未在 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u079aa073\" id=\"u079aa073\"><span data-lake-id=\"u223e99b8\" id=\"u223e99b8\">package.json</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ucf3c8755\" id=\"ucf3c8755\"> 中声明的包（即幽灵依赖）。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"ua84196c4\" id=\"ua84196c4\"><span data-lake-id=\"u341979c3\" id=\"u341979c3\">建议将 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u2684919c\" id=\"u2684919c\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5cf6bd77\" id=\"u5cf6bd77\">depcheck</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u4f154de6\" id=\"u4f154de6\"> 集成到 CI 流程中，防止幽灵依赖混入代码库。</span></p><h3 data-lake-id=\"wAXCb\" id=\"wAXCb\"><span data-lake-id=\"uc2fad333\" id=\"uc2fad333\">3. 代码审查与规范</span></h3><ul list=\"u09ed0124\"><li fid=\"u85c485be\" data-lake-id=\"u17541ba5\" id=\"u17541ba5\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u47548657\" id=\"u47548657\">在 Code Review 中强制要求</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u62f38c45\" id=\"u62f38c45\">：每当引入一个新的 </span><code data-lake-id=\"udacf0801\" id=\"udacf0801\"><span data-lake-id=\"u67c1d02e\" id=\"u67c1d02e\">import</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u8c95a5e2\" id=\"u8c95a5e2\">，必须确保对应的包已在 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u9f8fd27f\" id=\"u9f8fd27f\"><span data-lake-id=\"u8439db94\" id=\"u8439db94\">package.json</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ub22d1928\" id=\"ub22d1928\"> 中。</span></li><li fid=\"u85c485be\" data-lake-id=\"u262e1c72\" id=\"u262e1c72\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uee0aea94\" id=\"uee0aea94\">使用依赖检测机器人</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u39c429fc\" id=\"u39c429fc\">：例如 Dependabot 或 Renovate，它们不仅能更新依赖，有时也能标记可疑的依赖使用。</span></li><li fid=\"u85c485be\" data-lake-id=\"ua8e79556\" id=\"ua8e79556\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u04562a15\" id=\"u04562a15\">制定团队规范</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u736c160f\" id=\"u736c160f\">：明确所有直接依赖必须显式声明，禁止利用间接依赖。</span></li></ul><h3 data-lake-id=\"v6WaP\" id=\"v6WaP\"><span data-lake-id=\"u740a9ef2\" id=\"u740a9ef2\">4. 构建工具配置辅助</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u81d447b7\" id=\"u81d447b7\"><span data-lake-id=\"u48f385fe\" id=\"u48f385fe\">虽然构建工具（Webpack、Vite）本身不直接阻止幽灵依赖，但可以通过一些配置辅助发现问题：</span></p><ul list=\"uf877d7cc\"><li fid=\"ud8d9513f\" data-lake-id=\"ub8547880\" id=\"ub8547880\"><span data-lake-id=\"u034f0ebc\" id=\"u034f0ebc\">在 Webpack 中开启 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u6b3ae48c\" id=\"u6b3ae48c\"><span data-lake-id=\"u7a2d20d4\" id=\"u7a2d20d4\">resolve.fallback</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u40b07539\" id=\"u40b07539\"> 时，如果使用了未声明的 Node.js 核心模块，可能会暴露幽灵依赖，但这不是主要手段。</span></li><li fid=\"ud8d9513f\" data-lake-id=\"uec8661af\" id=\"uec8661af\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue342eb93\" id=\"ue342eb93\">更推荐在 </span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ue2d1928c\" id=\"ue2d1928c\">打包前</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u38ce3793\" id=\"u38ce3793\"> 通过 ESLint 或 depcheck 拦截问题。</span></li></ul><h3 data-lake-id=\"A7uW6\" id=\"A7uW6\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3db4b4dd\" id=\"u3db4b4dd\">5. 依赖锁文件与定期清理</span></h3><ul list=\"u51d0ed26\"><li fid=\"u35096e3e\" data-lake-id=\"u8db89784\" id=\"u8db89784\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ued79f3e9\" id=\"ued79f3e9\">提交锁文件</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ue58f4c7b\" id=\"ue58f4c7b\">（</span><code data-lake-id=\"u2ad6e61e\" id=\"u2ad6e61e\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue742c179\" id=\"ue742c179\">package-lock.json</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ue1a17a66\" id=\"ue1a17a66\"> / </span><code data-lake-id=\"ue68704ee\" id=\"ue68704ee\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub13db963\" id=\"ub13db963\">yarn.lock</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u6c5a2009\" id=\"u6c5a2009\"> / </span><code data-lake-id=\"u32172217\" id=\"u32172217\"><span data-lake-id=\"ua1fd3195\" id=\"ua1fd3195\">pnpm-lock.yaml</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u4dc619de\" id=\"u4dc619de\">）确保可重现的安装。</span></li><li fid=\"u35096e3e\" data-lake-id=\"u57e817aa\" id=\"u57e817aa\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3bd9e726\" id=\"u3bd9e726\">定期运行 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u831e5f7d\" id=\"u831e5f7d\"><span data-lake-id=\"u97c13af1\" id=\"u97c13af1\">npm prune</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u5ba9c320\" id=\"u5ba9c320\"> 或 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u85464fe3\" id=\"u85464fe3\"><span data-lake-id=\"u41288d1f\" id=\"u41288d1f\">yarn dedupe</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ufb1b87db\" id=\"ufb1b87db\"> 清理冗余依赖，但注意这并不能检测幽灵依赖，需要配合工具。</span></li></ul><h3 data-lake-id=\"qDOR8\" id=\"qDOR8\"><span data-lake-id=\"u95812139\" id=\"u95812139\">6. 使用 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u868e8fe8\" id=\"u868e8fe8\"><span data-lake-id=\"u16a5ffc2\" id=\"u16a5ffc2\">exports</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u273c1258\" id=\"u273c1258\"> 限制导入路径</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"ud402d70c\" id=\"ud402d70c\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4462d11f\" id=\"u4462d11f\">在库项目中，通过 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u6fa439f7\" id=\"u6fa439f7\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5a1a9e9a\" id=\"u5a1a9e9a\">package.json</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u3f140646\" id=\"u3f140646\"> 的 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u3dd5d368\" id=\"u3dd5d368\"><span data-lake-id=\"u72ccf01a\" id=\"u72ccf01a\">exports</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"uf7472868\" id=\"uf7472868\"> 字段限制外部只能访问特定的入口文件，可以间接避免使用者通过幽灵依赖访问内部模块。但这主要是控制 API 边界，并非直接解决幽灵依赖问题。</span></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"uktEd\" id=\"uktEd\"><span data-lake-id=\"ud34407f6\" id=\"ud34407f6\">推荐组合实践</span></h2><ul list=\"u3bba896a\"><li fid=\"u00fc4f71\" data-lake-id=\"u384fe1cb\" id=\"u384fe1cb\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u3e941e36\" id=\"u3e941e36\">开发环境</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u13771dd6\" id=\"u13771dd6\">：使用 pnpm 作为包管理器 + ESLint </span><code data-lake-id=\"uebf1c54d\" id=\"uebf1c54d\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4b59f92b\" id=\"u4b59f92b\">import/no-extraneous-dependencies</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"ud174a0b2\" id=\"ud174a0b2\"> 规则实时提示。</span></li><li fid=\"u00fc4f71\" data-lake-id=\"u733dd538\" id=\"u733dd538\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ue380c957\" id=\"ue380c957\">CI 环境</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u455f3d8b\" id=\"u455f3d8b\">：运行 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u467e2158\" id=\"u467e2158\"><span data-lake-id=\"uee44f745\" id=\"uee44f745\">depcheck</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u695a74f4\" id=\"u695a74f4\"> 或 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u97c93672\" id=\"u97c93672\"><span data-lake-id=\"ubb71c6a4\" id=\"ubb71c6a4\">eslint</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u854eb50b\" id=\"u854eb50b\"> 检查，确保没有幽灵依赖。</span></li><li fid=\"u00fc4f71\" data-lake-id=\"uf1a88790\" id=\"uf1a88790\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u6959aa79\" id=\"u6959aa79\">定期维护</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u244e2094\" id=\"u244e2094\">：每月执行一次 </span><code data-lake-id=\"u037e73a4\" id=\"u037e73a4\"><span data-lake-id=\"u180679e4\" id=\"u180679e4\">depcheck</span></code><span data-lake-id=\"u57938ce1\" id=\"u57938ce1\"> 并清理未使用的依赖。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"u77f3cbc5\" id=\"u77f3cbc5\"><span data-lake-id=\"u91af23ef\" id=\"u91af23ef\">通过这些实践，可以大大降低项目对幽灵依赖的隐性依赖，使依赖关系清晰、构建稳定，提高代码的可维护性和可移植性。</span></p>","word_count":1062,"slug":"onpacxu8q4nh2csx","type":"Doc","title":"在避免幽灵依赖上，有哪些实践？","public":1,"cover":null,"custom_cover":null,"description":"幽灵依赖（Phantom Dependency）是指项目中直接使用了某个 npm 包，但这个包并未在 package.json 中显式声明为依赖。由于该包被其他已声明的依赖所依赖（即作为间接依赖），因此当前项目的 node_modules 中确实存在它，代码可以正常运行。然而一旦间接依赖升级或...","custom_description":"","format":"lake","status":1,"read_status":1,"editor_meta":"{\"codeblock\":3}","user_id":200222,"created_at":"2026-02-28T08:03:18.000Z","updated_at":"2026-03-06T08:24:07.000Z","published_at":"2026-02-28T08:07:44.000Z","first_published_at":"2026-02-28T08:07:43.858Z","content_updated_at":"2026-02-28T08:07:44.000Z","id":258591945},"doc_digest":"XLoXGXaiGgsecPXeq64V6A4Y4Gg"}